info.headline: High Wind Warning issued November 16 at 3:25AM EST until November 16 at 1:00PM EST by NWS Miami
info.description: ...HIGH WIND WARNING IN EFFECT UNTIL 1 PM EST THIS AFTERNOON... * WHAT...East winds 25 to 40 mph with gusts up to 60 mph. * WHERE...Coastal Palm Beach County, Coastal Broward County and Coastal Miami Dade County. * WHEN...Until 1 PM EST this afternoon. * IMPACTS...Damaging winds will blow down trees and power lines. Widespread power outages are expected. Travel will be difficult, especially for high profile vehicles.
info.instruction: People should avoid being outside in forested areas and around trees and branches. If possible, remain in the lower levels of your home during the windstorm, and avoid windows. Use caution if you must drive.
